original: Lindblom, Sixten Carleson, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 14/3/98 i Lysekil av tandl. Carl August L. o. Valborg Elvira Lindberg. G. 40 m. Sonja Engström. Barn i föreg. äkt.: Jackie f. 22, fil. kand.; i nuv. äkt.: Carl 41, Birgitta 43. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. latin 17, stud. v. Karol. inst. 18, tandl :kand. 20, tandl. 23. Prakt, i Gbg sed. 23, tillika i Marstrand sed. 37. Hobbies: skytte o. simning. Erövrat ett flert. priser i skytte, idr :Gm, lägre årtals-Gm, miniatyrgevärskytteGm, Gbgs skyttegilles Gm, elitsimmarm. 47.
translated:
Lindblom, Sixten Carleson, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 14/3/98 in Lysekil to dentist Carl August L. and Valborg Elvira Lindberg. Married in 1940 to Sonja Engström. Children from previous marriage: Jackie b. 1922, Bachelor of Arts; from current marriage: Carl b. 1941, Birgitta b. 1943. 

Education: High school diploma from Gothenburg Latin School in 1917, studied at Karolinska Institute in 1918, received dentist degree in 1920, dentist license in 1923. 

Professional experience: Practiced in Gothenburg since 1923, also in Marstrand since 1937. 

Hobbies: Shooting and swimming. Has won several prizes in shooting competitions, including year-based and miniature rifle shooting championships and Gothenburg Shooting Guild championship. Also accomplished swimmer, achieving elite status in 1947.
